{"tid":1476493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂] 屬於香港人既記錄簿，大家幫幫手填滿佢","createTime":"2019-08-15T23:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T00:08:54.000Z","uid":232014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54391afc335dd2e12eeb0dbd3af14ab07d8e4d85","tid":1476493,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:37:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我發現香港人實在係太善忘，又或者係因為每日發生既突發事實在太多，成日都唔記得哂之前發生過啲咩重大事件。就好似<span style=\"color: red;\">海傍送中，葉虎架車</span>，咁重要既事而家已經一字不提。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以而家我想大家一齊講返每一件事出黎，然後有冇人識整網站可以將每一件事都放入一個屬於香港人既網，等香港人得閒就攞出黎回顧下，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再掀返起大家616既果團火！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>暫時我有9個大主題：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「革命」因由：</span>林鄭係都要送中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">市民抗爭手法：</span>遊行，衝立法會，罷工，塞機場塞鐵，前線勇武，圍警總，816撳錢...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警察濫暴/捕：</span>大把，有排搵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作：</span>721元朗，仲有北角，荃灣？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府既無能：</span>林鄭同盧偉聰錄音機，李家超立會同記者會既錄音機，仲有建制既謬論，何君堯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聯署同聲明：</span>好多，好似有人整合哂？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">外國既聲援：</span>英國美國加拿大法國澳洲啲相攞哂出黎，仲有攬炒巴既standwithhk<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲們既謬論：</span>Facebook，其他媒體相信大家都backup左唔少<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">社評：</span>社會有地位既聲音，例如何韻詩係聯合國既發言<br />\n<br />\n每一個主題都好多好多材料，我自己真係搵唔哂咁多，畢竟2個月個個禮拜都有野爆出黎，所以真係要靠咁多位喇！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有咩主題要加？我諗緊「義士重大事件」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港重大事件回顧tg:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/letsnotforgethk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fletsnotforgethk&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=2038ac68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/letsnotforgethk</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家發揮下你地既記憶，一齊記低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用返同一個格式，方便大家睇同做記錄：</span><br />\n<br />\n612<br />\n<br />\n三罷<br />\n中信<br />\n有個義士企係到就比幾個速龍推地下 禁住黎打"},{"pid":"e7ca24bcfc8f7ab1042506880749e3928c821c87","tid":1476493,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:37:44.000Z","msg":"69<br />\n<br />\n第一次圍立會<br />\n第一次比狗清場"},{"pid":"66dad4edb45e89e7786b81e2c9b178f88eaeb317","tid":1476493,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:37:48.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅機會啊！！十八區we connect，８２３和理非<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人鏈</span></span></strong>，萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a>"},{"pid":"6c3fe15383012d4610a2cd6ffef09fe59e9b25a2","tid":1476493,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:38:11.000Z","msg":"616 <br />\n<br />\n二百萬人遊行"},{"pid":"198b2ba6aab0b485f4af5a69f8faf90dc57a2f45","tid":1476493,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:38:42.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n<br />\n三罷<br />\n「交通意外」"},{"pid":"3d3a28ebd53512e50a1461af74be8ef710473ba0","tid":1476493,"uid":232014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T23:39: